Arithmetic Operators
Addition: +
Subtraction: -
Multiplication: *
Division: /
Modulus (Remainder): %
Increment: ++
Decrement: --
Assignment Operators
Assignment: =
Addition Assignment: +=
Subtraction Assignment: -=
Multiplication Assignment: *=
Division Assignment: /=
Modulus Assignment: %=
Comparison Operators
Equal to: ==
Not equal to: !=
Strict equal to: ===
Strict not equal to: !==
Greater than: >
Less than: <
Greater than or equal to: >=
Less than or equal to: <=
Logical Operators
Logical AND: &&
Logical OR: ||
Logical NOT: !
Bitwise Operators
Bitwise AND: &
Bitwise OR: |
Bitwise XOR: ^
Bitwise NOT: ~
Left shift: <<
Sign-propagating right shift: >>
Zero-fill right shift: >>>
Conditional (Ternary) Operator
condition ? expr1 : expr2
String Operators
Concatenation: +
Type Operators
typeof: typeof
Miscellaneous Operators
Comma: ,
Member Access: .
Square Bracket Access: []
Function Call: ()
New (object instantiation): new
Instanceof (type checking): instanceof